headline: Are Genuine Parts Shares Set for a Rebound After This Summer’s 4% Pullback?
summary: If you are sitting on the fence about Genuine Parts stock right now, you are not alone. It is the kind of company that can test your patience, sometimes drifting sideways and other times catching a tailwind just when it seems forgotten. Lately, the stock price has painted an interesting picture. Over the last month, shares dipped about 4.0%, even though they are still up an impressive 13.6% for the year.
